<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ ابْنُ مَنْظُورٍ في لِسَانِ العَرَب:</span> <span class="c1">" المُزُّ والمُزَّةُ والمُزَّاء: الخَمْرُ اللَّذِيذَةُ الطَّعْم، سُمِّيَتْ بِذَلِكَ لِلَذْعِهَا اللِّسَان "</span> ٠<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَنَقَلَ عَنْ بَعْضِ أَهْلِ اللُّغَةِ قَوْلَهُ:</span> <span class="c1">" المَزَّةُ بِفَتْحِ المِيم: الخمر "</span> ٠<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{لِسَانُ العَرَب: ٣٠٧/ ٥}</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>الذَّهَب/ع،<span class="c5"> الجَوَاهِر/ع:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الأَلمَاس:</span> هُوَ مُا نُسَمِّيهِ الأَلمَاظ ٠ <span class="c3">{لِسَانُ العَرَب: ٢١٣/ ٦}</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">رَأَى:</span> <span class="c4">[انْظُرِ الْعَينَ بحَرْفِ الْعَين]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>